<HEAD>Government Orders U.S. Carriers To Tighten Security</HEAD>
<HEAD>With PM-Flight 103, Bjt</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By EDITH M. LEDERER</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>LONDON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
